PROJECT UNDERSTANDING

Vouchiqo is NOT a coupon website.

Vouchiqo is:

* Verified Deals Platform
* Merchant Growth Platform
* Local Offer Discovery Platform
* Expired Coupon Revival Platform
* Savings Analytics Platform

Brand Promise:

Verified Deals.
Real Savings.

Core Experience:

Trust First.
Savings Second.
Technology Third.

The website should feel like:

* Stripe
* Shopify
* Notion
* Linear
* Razorpay
* Airbnb Business

Avoid:

* CouponDunia look
* Cheap discount website look
* Flashy e-commerce style
* Gambling style urgency
* Excessive animations

